Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是谁的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.52,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳进去跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.88,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起来 破坏掉这无理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不开这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.22,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到终幕我都要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.09,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 这不是玩笑
Comment: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.95,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Comment: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.63,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.15,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}去舍弃掉吧 rulers
Comment: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.07,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Comment: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.60,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,波打つざわめき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.12,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,彩度を失う記憶に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.71,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,願いは幾度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.47,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,数えてみたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.16,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,晦冥を揺らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:51.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,希望に似てた歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.80,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,祈れば砂のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:58.33,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,零れ落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.00,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.39,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,密かに息吹く想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:09.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた鋼に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.41,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,意味もなく　際限なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.32,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,廻るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:20.10,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,世界が引き裂かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:23.83,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,結んだ手離さずいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.26,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,歪んだ支配が朽ちても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,その名を呼ぶの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:33.97,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,綺麗なアイじゃなくっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.92,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,息をするたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.98,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,あなた求めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:46.21,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,どこへはぐれてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.45,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.60,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,起起落落的杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,在失去色彩的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.71,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈求了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,只是数一数
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,也混身震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,像是那波动黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:51.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,希望似的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.80,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈祷的话就会像沙砾一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:58.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,凋零飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.00,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我一直都知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.39,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,那呼吸中不为人知的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:09.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,接触到了生锈的钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,没有意义 没有终点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.32,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,循环
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:20.10,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算世界崩裂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:23.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我们握紧的手也不会分开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.26,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算扭曲的统治腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我也会呼唤那个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:33.97,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算不是美丽的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我只要一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,便在寻求着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:46.21,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,无论迷失在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.45,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,再一次
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
